Yes, an Internal ESG Committee has been formed. The Composition of the Committee is as follows: 
1) Mr. Arjuun Guuha, Whole Time Director – Chairman; 
2) Mr. Shardul Doshi, Chief Financial Officer – Member; 
3) Mr. Sumer Thakkar, General Manager-Sales & Strategy – Member; 
4) Ms. Shalaka Ovalekar – Company Secretary & VP Legal – Member.

